<function>

access:   public

name: publicHref

param: Solar_Uri_Public|string, $spec

param: bool, $raw, false

return: string

</function>

Returns an href to a public resource.

* Parameters:

 * Solar_Uri_Public|string //$spec//: The public resource href specification.

 * bool //$raw//: Return the resource string without escaping (default false).

* Returns string